# ext-bb-notification-center-ng


Version: **3.8.0**

Default extension for notifications center.

* vendor-bb-uib-tooltip

## Example

```javascript
<!-- widget's model.xml -->
<property name="extension" viewHint="text-input,admin">
 <value type="string">ext-bb-notification-center-ng</value>
</property>
```
